唔見師兄話over左既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本個樓主就自雙矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n標題話睇過美欺全盛就唔會話C羅勁<br />\n但內文又承認牙朗勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a29d4213b34ccba4633bcf86d8155ddbc8ef544","tid":502901,"uid":83933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T14:34:02.000Z","msg":"師兄可以出個林敏驄版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec5bcfbdf04d3015f07b13785f6a41b8623c0a3c","tid":502901,"uid":53855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T14:45:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚過癮"},{"pid":"9ee4b104996b4aba3f13e389d34200f0cab2df38","tid":502901,"uid":53855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T14:45:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得啦，知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c0a0224d946bc4f5b611313c85a8deea57c36a","tid":502901,"uid":116896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T14:46:40.000Z","msg":"咁美斯係勁過卡卡"},{"pid":"cbbe2fc0e35c8fa0f7fda52f9598e0728e58440b","tid":502901,"uid":84834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T16:35:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁美斯係勁過卡卡</blockquote><br />\n依家新例正負皮代表一切呀，<br />\n連最識波既連登仔都唔認同美斯&gt;卡卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043299c8bb10b3e723c3b21e80f9